Question goes here.
}

li.p:
If part of a short answer is inappropriate, (for example, part (b)) use

  \begin{enumerate}
  \item Answer to part (a)
  \iinoshrtans
  \item Answer to part (c)
  \end{enumerate}

section.p:
Use 

  \WPHint{
  blah blah blah.
  }

Then, to add a figure with neither number nor caption, use

  \begin{stayfig}
  \input{1-2dslgnp003fig}
  \end{stayfig}

